{
  "video_id": "3x5VAg1HJIg",
  "title": "Meet the Intern Who Wrote Solitaire for Microsoft",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 316.0,
      "end_time": 2385.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Solitaire is one of the most popular"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2386.0,
      "end_time": 4695.0,
      "text": "computer games of all time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4695.0,
      "end_time": 7548.0,
      "text": "and we went to find the guy who created it."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7548.0,
      "end_time": 8545.0,
      "text": "(tires screech)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8545.0,
      "end_time": 11530.0,
      "text": "(doorbell rings)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11530.0,
      "end_time": 12234.0,
      "text": "- Yes, may I help you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12234.0,
      "end_time": 13150.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Are you the person that wrote"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 13150.0,
      "end_time": 14826.0,
      "text": "solitaire for Microsoft?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 14826.0,
      "end_time": 17347.0,
      "text": "- Yes, but that was a long time ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 17347.0,
      "end_time": 18180.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] We gotta talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 18180.0,
      "end_time": 19120.0,
      "text": "Can we come in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 19130.0,
      "end_time": 19989.0,
      "text": "Great, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 19989.0,
      "end_time": 22739.0,
      "text": "(cheerful music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 25764.0,
      "end_time": 26884.0,
      "text": "('80's pop music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 26884.0,
      "end_time": 28939.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Alright, this is Wes."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 28939.0,
      "end_time": 32174.0,
      "text": "- I'm Wes Cherry, and I wrote Windows Solitaire."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 32174.0,
      "end_time": 35491.0,
      "text": "I wrote the game in 1988 as an intern."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 35491.0,
      "end_time": 37442.0,
      "text": "Internships at Microsoft were really an all"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 37442.0,
      "end_time": 39556.0,
      "text": "encompassing thing, but I squoze it in there"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 39556.0,
      "end_time": 41867.0,
      "text": "in the few little hours of my free time."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 41867.0,
      "end_time": 43210.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] For those who need a refresher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 43210.0,
      "end_time": 46106.0,
      "text": "Solitaire was played on the computer using a mouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 46106.0,
      "end_time": 48970.0,
      "text": "Cards are pulled from the deck in an effort"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 48970.0,
      "end_time": 50575.0,
      "text": "to stack cards in order by suit."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 50575.0,
      "end_time": 53417.0,
      "text": "And if you won, you got an awesome display of cards"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 53417.0,
      "end_time": 55250.0,
      "text": "cascading towards you."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 56145.0,
      "end_time": 57206.0,
      "text": "- [Wes] I came up with the idea to write"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 57206.0,
      "end_time": 59044.0,
      "text": "Solitaire for Windows out of boredom, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 59044.0,
      "end_time": 61500.0,
      "text": "There wasn't many games right at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 61500.0,
      "end_time": 62869.0,
      "text": "so we had to make them."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 62869.0,
      "end_time": 66554.0,
      "text": "In the mid to late ’90's was just when people started"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 66554.0,
      "end_time": 68390.0,
      "text": "really getting computers in their home."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 68390.0,
      "end_time": 71152.0,
      "text": "Microsoft officially said that Solitaire was there to"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 71152.0,
      "end_time": 73466.0,
      "text": "teach people how to use the mouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 73466.0,
      "end_time": 74619.0,
      "text": "But, in reality it was just really just"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 74620.0,
      "end_time": 77100.0,
      "text": "something to have fun with."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 77100.0,
      "end_time": 77927.0,
      "text": "Before they ever released Windows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 77927.0,
      "end_time": 80287.0,
      "text": "of course Bill Gates got a shot at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 80287.0,
      "end_time": 81423.0,
      "text": "His biggest complaint was that Solitaire"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 81423.0,
      "end_time": 82970.0,
      "text": "was too hard to win."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 82970.0,
      "end_time": 84282.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And once people figured out the mouse"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 84282.0,
      "end_time": 86252.0,
      "text": "it became a favorite past time."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 86252.0,
      "end_time": 88770.0,
      "text": "- The number of hours wasted on Solitaire"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 88770.0,
      "end_time": 90890.0,
      "text": "is really countless."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 90890.0,
      "end_time": 94390.0,
      "text": "I can say that right after Solitaire was released in 1990"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 94391.0,
      "end_time": 95957.0,
      "text": "there was a world recession."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 95957.0,
      "end_time": 97440.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] So many people were playing it in the workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 97440.0,
      "end_time": 100954.0,
      "text": "that Wes came up with what he called “the boss key.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 100954.0,
      "end_time": 103666.0,
      "text": "- Press the special key and a spreadsheet was come up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 103667.0,
      "end_time": 106700.0,
      "text": "so it made it look like you were doing real work."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 106700.0,
      "end_time": 107986.0,
      "text": "But, Microsoft made me take it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 107986.0,
      "end_time": 108819.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Considering this game"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 108819.0,
      "end_time": 109798.0,
      "text": "has been around for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 109798.0,
      "end_time": 111964.0,
      "text": "you must have made a ton of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 111964.0,
      "end_time": 114262.0,
      "text": "- I was not paid not a single cent."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 114262.0,
      "end_time": 117163.0,
      "text": "At one time I said if I only got a penny per copy"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 117163.0,
      "end_time": 118928.0,
      "text": "I would be very rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 118928.0,
      "end_time": 121865.0,
      "text": "So far, only 14 people have made good on that."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 121865.0,
      "end_time": 124363.0,
      "text": "I'm still waiting for the rest of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 124363.0,
      "end_time": 125828.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Well, you heard the man."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 125828.0,
      "end_time": 127207.0,
      "text": "Do you still work with computers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 127207.0,
      "end_time": 129470.0,
      "text": "- I work with Apple now."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 129470.0,
      "end_time": 130987.0,
      "text": "Apples, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 130987.0,
      "end_time": 132337.0,
      "text": "And I own a cidery."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 132337.0,
      "end_time": 134750.0,
      "text": "(crunching)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 134750.0,
      "end_time": 135688.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Ah, Wes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 135688.0,
      "end_time": 137362.0,
      "text": "there's something behind you."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 137362.0,
      "end_time": 138595.0,
      "text": "Wes, run!"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 138595.0,
      "end_time": 140928.0,
      "text": "(pounding)"
    }
  ]
}